lx4p

Class LXJSONElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • lx4p.LXJSONElement

  • public class LXJSONElement
extends java.lang.Object
    LXJSONElement is a class that holds an element of a JSON object tree. A tree of LXJSONElements is created by a LXJSONParser from a JSON string. Each leaf element holds a tag/value. An LXJSONElement can also hold sub-elements.
    Version:
    001
    Author:
    Claude Heintz
    See Also:
    LXJSONParser
